    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the S65 4.0L V8 engine with its distinct 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a lightning-fast M-DCT 7-speed dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis dynamics are enhanced by Electronic Damper Control (EDC), offering precise compression and rebound adjustment. This example has been meticulously maintained",
