    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a discerning buyer seeking a well-maintained and reliable daily driver. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory finish, exhibiting a deep luster with only minor, negligible imperfections consistent with careful use. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of significant curbing. Inside, the cabin remains a highlight; the premium upholstery is clean and well-preserved, and the interior trim shows very little wear. All power features, including the sunroof, infotainment system, and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car has been treated with the utmost care. It has a documented service history, featuring regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake service. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the suspension remains tight and responsive, offering a composed ride quality. Included with the sale are two sets of keys and the original owner\u2019s manuals. This is a solid, turn-key vehicle that has been kept to a high standard and is ready for its next chapter.",
